Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:24.05,Luna,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Grand Equestian Pony Summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.63,0:00:27.89,Celestia,,0,0,0,,You delegates have traveled far and wide
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:29.55,Celestia,,0,0,0,,to represent your cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:33.28,Celestia,,0,0,0,,As we seek to celebrate and learn from all the unique places
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:36.31,Celestia,,0,0,0,,that make up our wonderful land of Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:38.18,Celestia,,0,0,0,,At tonight's welcome reception
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.18,0:00:42.01,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence will dedicate this beatiful friendship statue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:44.62,Celestia,,0,0,0,,made up of gemstones from each of your home cities.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.32,0:00:56.05,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Now I'd like to turn things over to the one who organized the summit
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.05,0:00:57.86,Celestia,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight Sparkle
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.76,0:01:01.60,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Thank you everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.70,Twilight,,0,0,0,,With delegates from over 50 cities
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:07.64,Twilight,,0,0,0,,attending three days of conferences, receptions, and meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.64,0:01:11.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,This is the largest Grand Equestia Pony Summit yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.14,0:01:16.06,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And let me tell you: putting it all together has led to more than one sleepless night.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.06,0:01:18.39,Twilight,,0,0,0,,We're so excited to have you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:21.87,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And to learn more about life all across this great land of ours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:29.00,Twilight,,0,0,0,,And now my faithful assistant Spike would like to say a few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.72,0:01:33.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hello everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.17,0:01:35.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm here to help any way I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.81,0:01:38.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,So if there is anything I can do for any of you-
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.05,0:01:40.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We love you Princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.18,0:01:42.18,Somepony,,0,0,0,,We love all the princesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.27,0:01:47.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,I guess everypony loves a princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.24,0:02:36.36,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Spike!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:39.01,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:40.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,A little help…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.58,0:02:44.38,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Spike, we need you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.38,0:02:46.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Of course, what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:50.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,Whoa, what happened to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.32,0:02:53.40,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry, Spike, I just…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.83,0:02:59.18,Twilight,,0,0,0,,need a quick… nap. Napkin…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.18,0:03:01.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Tell the delegates I'll…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.80,0:03:05.32,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,She's been awake three straight days preparing for the summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:07.98,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,We need to make sure she gets some rest today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:11.95,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,She'll never be able to attend the welcome reception in this condition!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.95,0:03:15.71,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Can I count on you to see to it that she isn't disturbed?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:19.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,I promise! I won't let you down!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:38.81,Spike,,0,0,0,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:45.54,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.57,0:03:49.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.69,0:03:51.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can you keep it down a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.41,0:03:54.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.77,0:04:01.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'll give you bird seed! Worms! Anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.31,0:04:04.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,Just please stop singing before you wake the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.75,0:04:11.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,Huh, I can't believe that worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:31.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hi fellas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.47,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sorry to break up your game, but
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.47,0:04:37.15,Spike,,0,0,0,,there's sort of an important diplomatic summit kind of thingy going on, and
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.42,Spike,,0,0,0,,it involves a princess needing her sleep, and, uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:43.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,maybe you could move your game somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.29,0:04:50.72,Spike,,0,0,0,,The princess thanks you for your understanding!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:54.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Do you have to do this right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.52,0:04:59.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh no! Are those Dragonsneeze trees?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:04.49,Somepony,,0,0,0,,These are too top-heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't take much to take these beauties down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.94,0:05:10.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can't you just wait a few hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.07,0:05:12.87,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it's a public hazard, got my orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:18.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, I've got my orders too, from princess Twi… Twi… Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.93,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.93,0:05:24.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you say so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.55,0:05:26.99,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'll reckon they'll keep a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.28,0:05:30.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,Good thing that i've got princesses on my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.36,0:05:37.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.62,0:05:40.31,Spike,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.31,0:05:43.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,I really need you to stop right now! Oops.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.97,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Lemme guess, the noise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.97,0:05:49.71,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but we can't have a broken water main.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.03,Spike,,0,0,0,,Ugh, you couldn't do this yesterday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:56.14,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hey, pal, I'm just trying to make sure everything works smooth for the summit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.14,0:05:58.73,Spike,,0,0,0,,But there is no summit without princess Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.73,0:06:01.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,And she needs things to be kept quiet around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.78,0:06:02.94,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, if you don't mind, I'd…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.94,0:06:06.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Allright, allright, if that's how she wants it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.84,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But if something happens, it ain't my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:21.70,Spike,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight will be rested,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.70,0:06:23.43,Spike,,0,0,0,,Princess Cadence will be proud,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.43,0:06:26.91,Spike,,0,0,0,,and princess Spike deserves a little reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.59,0:06:29.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Princess Spike…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.28,0:06:38.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.14,0:06:39.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:42.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,My friend here, the distinguished pony from up Manehattan, and I →
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:47.41,Somepony,,0,0,0,,are in a bit of a pickle, and we need the princess Twilight to resolve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:49.67,Spike,,0,0,0,,Can you talk a little quieter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.67,0:06:51.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,And maybe come back later?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:52.58,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure, now, gosh, I wish we could,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:57.33,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but we're both supposed to give speeches about our local economies in five minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.33,0:06:59.48,Somepony,,0,0,0,,and we've been booked in the same hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.48,0:07:00.73,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I had the room first.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:03.46,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And let's be honest, my speech is more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Point of order there sir, but I think you'll find it
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.13,0:07:09.37,Somepony,,0,0,0,,my speech is the more important one, dontcha know.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.37,0:07:13.17,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Look, youse is gonna have a lot of unhappy delegates on your hooves
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.17,0:07:16.80,Somepony,,0,0,0,,unless we get a ruling from princess Twilight right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.30,0:07:24.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,Let me see what I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.79,0:07:38.80,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Does something need scheduling?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.80,0:07:40.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.51,0:07:42.96,Spike,,0,0,0,,Two delegates have speeches booked in the same hall.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.96,0:07:44.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,What do I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.11,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Okay, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.77,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Just put the hay in the apple and eat the candle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.90,0:07:54.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,I need an answer,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,but Twilight can't even think straight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:57.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.11,0:07:59.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.80,0:08:04.39,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.39,0:08:05.35,Somepony,,0,0,0,,What did she say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.35,0:08:06.66,Somepony,,0,0,0,,She picked me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.66,0:08:10.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hey hey hey, let's not be too hasty there good sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.27,0:08:12.28,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I got a feeling she went with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.28,0:08:14.04,Somepony,,0,0,0,,He-hey, if she didn't pick me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.04,0:08:17.76,Somepony,,0,0,0,,it ain't hard to see that as an insult to all of Manehattan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:18.86,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You know what I'm saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.86,0:08:22.31,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And it'd sure be a shame see something like a scheduling issue
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.31,0:08:25.72,Somepony,,0,0,0,,create a nasty old rift between Whinnyapolis and Ponyville!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.72,0:08:28.41,Somepony,,0,0,0,,So, what did the princess say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.41,0:08:30.52,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Come on now, spit it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.38,0:08:33.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,She said that, well…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.25,0:08:36.25,Spike,,0,0,0,,She said that you… She wants you to…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.25,0:08:37.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Share it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:42.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,If that's what the princess wants, what are ya gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.69,0:08:44.57,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The princess is always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.57,0:08:47.24,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Listen, no hard feelings, this is not about you and me…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.24,0:08:48.55,Somepony,,0,0,0,,…I have no hard feelings…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.45,0:08:53.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,Now, back to more important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:09:00.78,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Combining those two talks was a disaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:04.17,Somepony,,0,0,0,,The hall was overcrowded and the speakers just shouted over each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.17,0:09:05.19,Spike,,0,0,0,,Huh? But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Why would the princess have made such a decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.01,0:09:19.80,Spike,,0,0,0,,By order of princess Twilight, be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.95,0:09:27.89,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I was really looking forward to the "don't spend all your bits" speech,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:32.13,Somepony,,0,0,0,,but when I went into the hall, a pony had taken my seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.13,0:09:35.50,Somepony,,0,0,0,,A pony who used to be my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.50,0:09:37.33,Spike,,0,0,0,,Your friend took your seat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.67,0:09:38.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Big deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.60,0:09:39.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:42.53,Somepony,,0,0,0,,No offense, but I don't need some random dragon's opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.53,0:09:45.77,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I want to hear what princess Twilight thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.86,0:09:58.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,The princess says, no friendship should end over a seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.29,0:10:00.04,Spike,,0,0,0,,You should forgive your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.41,0:10:01.96,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.96,0:10:04.94,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, the princess is so wise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.59,0:10:10.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,I could tell these delegates anything as long as they think it came from Twilight!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:15.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Allright, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.95,0:10:59.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, how can princess Twilight be of service?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:03.73,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Well, as host city, the Canterlot delegation feels it's only right
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.73,0:11:07.89,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,that we should get passes to every meeting and party, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.89,0:11:09.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, that doesn't seem fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:13.32,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean, princess Twilight doesn't think that seems fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:16.08,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.08,0:11:19.09,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,It was worth the try though, wasn't it, chap?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:24.21,Spike,,0,0,0,,This is great. I'm just to care of a whole bunch of stuff that Twilight
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.21,0:11:26.89,Spike,,0,0,0,,won't have to worry about when she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.89,0:11:29.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wonder if anypony else needs the princess's help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.03,0:11:39.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,If I can check a few of these meetings off Twilight's schedule,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.23,0:11:43.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,then when she wakes up she won't have to think about anything but the reception.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.03,0:11:51.71,Spike,,0,0,0,,Says here you have a meeting with princess Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:53.85,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yuppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.85,0:11:56.91,Somepony,,0,0,0,,She wanted me to prep her on all the different gemstones
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.91,0:12:00.69,Somepony,,0,0,0,,in the Citizens of Equestria statue before the reception tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.82,0:12:02.07,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.71,0:12:07.57,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Well, I'd rather, um, tell the princess directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.57,0:12:11.39,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, if it helps you can call me princess Spike.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.13,Spike,,0,0,0,,No no no, it it's alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:17.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,The princess asked me to take care of a few things for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.74,0:12:19.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,That's why I came to find you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.93,Somepony,,0,0,0,,If you say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.93,0:12:23.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,The princess says so!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:28.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's start with topaz.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.13,0:12:32.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm here for your 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.17,0:12:37.46,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You?! But I'm supposed to be briefing princess Twilight on a progress with the water main.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.46,0:12:39.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,I speak for the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.16,0:12:41.85,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow. Can I start fixing it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.85,0:12:44.22,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm getting a little worried, to be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.22,0:12:46.50,Spike,,0,0,0,,Actually, Twilight still needs her rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:49.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,And a no noise policy is still on effect for a few more hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.88,0:12:50.45,Spike,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.52,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Hey Spike, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:58.83,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nah, you know, just setting them up and knocking them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.83,0:13:00.01,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.01,0:13:03.40,Spike,,0,0,0,,Not only have I kept things quiet so Twilight could sleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:05.20,Spike,,0,0,0,,I also took care of all her afternoon meetings,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:08.57,Spike,,0,0,0,,so she won't have to worry about them when she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:11.20,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she'd want you doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.20,0:13:13.96,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,There are so many things to keep track of at this summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.96,0:13:16.38,Spike,,0,0,0,,Nah, don't worry. I got it covered.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.38,0:13:20.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,I know Twilight so well it's easy to make decisions like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.16,0:13:22.15,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:25.95,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for keeping Twilight's stress level down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.95,0:13:29.44,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,As long as that's the real reason you're doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:32.17,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, why else would I be doing it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.17,0:13:35.83,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,You're not enjoying speaking for Twilight a little bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.83,0:13:38.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,Enjoying it? No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:42.55,Spike,,0,0,0,,The only things I'm doing by order of the princess are for the good of the summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.32,0:13:55.59,Spike,,0,0,0,,By order of the princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:02.22,Spike,,0,0,0,,By order of the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:10.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,By order of the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.47,0:14:15.64,Spike,,0,0,0,,Princess life is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.01,0:14:22.40,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,It sure is, but it's also hard work, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:23.97,Spike,,0,0,0,,Eh, it's not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:28.53,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,Spike, I'm concerned you might be abusing your relationship with Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:32.23,Spike,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about? I'm a great princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.85,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean, Twilight's a great princess!\NAnd I've been working hard to help her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:37.66,Spike,,0,0,0,,When two delegates had a falling out,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.66,0:14:39.27,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm the one who fixed their friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:43.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,I listened to that pony droning on about gems for 45 minutes so Twilight wouldn't have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:46.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm of the polo match away from the town so Twilight could sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.88,Spike,,0,0,0,,And I didn't even eat that delicious looking statue.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.88,0:14:51.36,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm a decision making master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:58.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,Okay… So maybe I did get a little carried away making decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,But it's not like anything bad happend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.92,0:15:24.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,This is unexpected.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.67,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I'll go shut up the main,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.67,0:15:27.36,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,you'll get rid of the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.59,0:16:03.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,At least the statue is okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.65,0:16:07.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.05,0:16:09.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.95,0:16:19.60,Spike,,0,0,0,,Oh, bless me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.40,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Oh my…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.82,0:16:30.69,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,What is the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.69,0:16:32.75,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, y'see,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.22,0:16:34.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,there was this polo game, and…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.78,0:16:39.06,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,How could you let a water main burst on Canterlot's most important day?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:40.38,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.38,0:16:43.27,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Princess Twilight said to stop working on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.27,0:16:44.90,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,And what about these trees?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:47.93,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,I ordered them trimmed to avoid just such a situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.93,0:16:50.30,Somepony,,0,0,0,,But the princess told me to stop, bub!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.30,0:16:53.11,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Why would the princess make such horrible decisions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.56,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,This all could have been prevented!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.02,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please, everypony, listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.02,0:17:00.11,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry all this happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.11,0:17:01.73,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,What are you apologizing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:04.12,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,These were princess Twilight's awful decisions!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:08.17,Somepony,,0,0,0,,I'm about to blow my stack on princess Twilight, I'll tell you that for nothin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.17,0:17:09.10,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Yeah, me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.10,0:17:13.89,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,I'll not let princess Twilight give Canterlot a bad name in the eyes of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.89,0:17:17.64,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Come on, everypony! Let's go give her a piece of our minds!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.15,0:17:20.87,Spike,,0,0,0,,Please! You've got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.86,0:17:30.29,Spike,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.49,0:17:34.06,Spike,,0,0,0,,I mean, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:35.51,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,What is it now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:38.27,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,There's an angry mob here that demands satisfaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:41.68,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's just that, uh, we don't want to wake the princess, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.68,0:17:43.07,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Wake her?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.07,0:17:45.62,Somepony,,0,0,0,,You're tellin' me that she's asleep?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:56.23,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Princess, we must speak at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.23,0:18:00.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,She is SLEEPING!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.13,0:18:13.23,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you're here, Spike. We've got a lot to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.23,0:18:15.37,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Do you know if the water main was fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.05,Spike,,0,0,0,,You seem well-rested!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.05,0:18:20.68,Twilight,,0,0,0,,I haven't slept like that since I was a filly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.68,0:18:21.74,Spike,,0,0,0,,You haven't?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.74,0:18:24.56,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, at least I got one thing right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:27.48,Spike,,0,0,0,,And, it was the one thing Cadance asked of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.48,0:18:29.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,Maybe I did do a good job today!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.52,0:18:36.67,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Fancy Pants, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.67,0:18:40.22,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Don't play games with me, princess, you know why I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.79,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Is this about the special privileges you wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.79,0:18:45.32,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Because this seems a little extreme!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.32,0:18:47.37,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,The special privileges?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.37,0:18:50.66,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,The last thing on my mind is special privileges!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.27,0:18:53.38,Twilight,,0,0,0,,What's going on, Spike?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.38,0:18:54.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,Um…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.17,0:18:56.78,Spike,,0,0,0,,you needed to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,And princess Cadance told me you weren't to be disturbed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.14,0:19:01.16,Spike,,0,0,0,,Then there was this bird, and, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.63,Spike,,0,0,0,,long story short,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.63,0:19:06.10,Spike,,0,0,0,,I made a few decisions on your behalf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.62,Twilight,,0,0,0,,A few decisions?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.62,0:19:13.26,Spike,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe more than a few, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.26,0:19:16.34,Spike,,0,0,0,,I had good intentions, honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:18.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,Until I…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.62,0:19:20.41,Spike,,0,0,0,,didn't anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.41,0:19:22.01,Spike,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.01,0:19:24.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,I guess I got a little carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.58,0:19:30.00,Spike,,0,0,0,,It, it just felt so good to have ponies caring about my opinions on such important matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.00,0:19:34.52,Spike,,0,0,0,,I guess I was just enjoying feeling like a princess…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.52,0:19:38.14,Twilight,,0,0,0,,Well, Spike, one of the most important things a princess can do
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.14,0:19:41.20,Twilight,,0,0,0,,is realize when she's made a mistake and fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:42.58,Spike,,0,0,0,,And how do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.59,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,You could start with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.61,0:19:50.95,Spike,,0,0,0,,Uh, hi there, everypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:55.62,Spike,,0,0,0,,So, I guess I owe you all a pretty big apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.62,0:20:01.44,Spike,,0,0,0,,It's funny: here we are at a summit that brings together ponies from all across Equestria,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.44,0:20:04.37,Spike,,0,0,0,,but then all I could think about was myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.37,0:20:10.14,Spike,,0,0,0,,You all came here to celebrate the things that make each of our cities so unique and special,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:14.51,Spike,,0,0,0,,but instead of getting into the spirit of things like all of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.51,0:20:18.82,Spike,,0,0,0,,I used my friend's position to make myself feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.92,0:20:36.20,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,The Canterlot ruby goes here, old sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.74,0:20:39.56,Somepony,,0,0,0,,And ours goes here, don't'cha know?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.12,0:20:57.91,Spike,,0,0,0,,Does this mean you forgive me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:59.26,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.26,0:21:03.98,Somepony,,0,0,0,,Y'know the whole idea of the statue is that when each of us plays our own small part,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:06.32,Somepony,,0,0,0,,it ends up as somethin' great.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:07.12,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Quite.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.12,0:21:11.73,FancyPants,,0,0,0,,Just like how all our cities make up the beautiful land of Equestria!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.73,0:21:15.19,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,I hereby dedicate the Citizens of Equestria statue
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.19,0:21:17.83,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,to everypony who plays their part,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:21.29,PrincessCadence,,0,0,0,,no matter how big or how small!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.69,0:21:27.69,Spike,,0,0,0,,Aw, come on!
